reduce

public UFraction reduce()
Method for simple reduction of fraction - each term from numerator and denominator is reduced (i.e. divided) by gcd (greatest common divisor) of all terms. Also, if denominator is real number, numerator is divided by it. Assumption is made that this fraction is valid.

Returns:
This object, which is result of operation
